## Per-claim sections

Use this template, one per major claim:

```
## Claim: <claim name (mirror strat-summary.md)>

**Current level:** L<1-4>
**Last updated:** YYYY-MM-DD

**Statement:** <one-sentence claim>

**What would change it (falsification criteria):**
- <criterion 1 — make it narrow enough to actually happen, not a bar so high it can never be met>
- <criterion 2>

**Untested contexts (your falsification surface):**
- <where you haven't tested this yet — the honest answer to "where could you be wrong?">

**Level promotion note:**
- <if L2: name both cases and their exact commonality>
- <if L3: name the forward prediction you made and which engagement confirmed it>
- <if L4: name the last time you actively tested this and how long it has held>

| Date       | Engagement / Source        | Direction      | Notes |
|------------|----------------------------|----------------|-------|
| YYYY-MM-DD | <engagement / call / etc.> | SUPPORTS / CONTRADICTS / NEUTRAL | <1-2 sentences> |
```

